What is the output of the following C code?
```c
int x = 5;
int *p = &x;
*p = 10;
printf("%d", x);
```

What is the output of the following C code?
```c
char str[] = "Hello";
char *p = str;
printf("%c", *(p+2));
```

What is the output of the following code?
```c
int a = 5;
printf("%d %d %d", a++, ++a, a);
```

What is the output of the following C++ code?
```cpp
std::vector<int> v = {1, 2, 3, 4, 5};
auto it = v.begin() + 2;
v.erase(it);
std::cout << v[2];
```

